| Express           | Django                     |
| ----------------- | -------------------------- |
| `npm install`     | `pip install`              |
| `node_modules`    | `venv`                     |
| `server.js`       | `manage.py`                |
| Routes            | `urls.py`                  |
| Controllers       | `views.py`                 |
| Mongoose Models   | `models.py`                |
| Prisma migrations | `python manage.py migrate` |

venv\Scripts\activate
python manage.py runserver
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser
python manage.py startapp <app_name>

# Django Commands Cheat Sheet

## Create a Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

## Activate Virtual Environment

### Windows PowerShell

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Windows CMD

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate.bat
```

### Mac/Linux

```bash
source venv/bin/activate
```

## Deactivate Virtual Environment

```bash
deactivate
```

---

## Install Django

```bash
pip install django
```

## Check Django Version

```bash
django-admin --version
```

## Save Dependencies

```bash
pip freeze > requirements.txt
```

## Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Create a Django Project

```bash
django-admin startproject config .
```

## Run Development Server

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

Run on a custom port:

```bash
python manage.py runserver 8001
```

---

## Create a Django App

```bash
python manage.py startapp home
```

Example apps:

```bash
python manage.py startapp students
python manage.py startapp accounts
python manage.py startapp products
```

---

## Database Migrations

Create migration files:

```bash
python manage.py makemigrations
```

Apply migrations:

```bash
python manage.py migrate
```

Show migration status:

```bash
python manage.py showmigrations
```

---

## Create Superuser

```bash
python manage.py createsuperuser
```

Admin URL:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/
```

---

## Django Shell

Open shell:

```bash
python manage.py shell
```

Exit shell:

```python
exit()
```

---

## Collect Static Files (Production)

```bash
python manage.py collectstatic
```

---

## Common URLs

Home:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
```

Admin:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/
```

Students Example:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/students/
```

---

## Typical Workflow

```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install django
django-admin startproject config .
python manage.py startapp home
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser
python manage.py runserver
```

---

## MERN â†’ Django Mapping

| MERN            | Django                     |
| --------------- | -------------------------- |
| npm install     | pip install                |
| node_modules    | venv                       |
| package.json    | requirements.txt           |
| Express App     | Django Project             |
| Feature Folder  | Django App                 |
| Mongoose Schema | Django Model               |
| Prisma Migrate  | makemigrations + migrate   |
| npm start       | python manage.py runserver |
| MongoDB Compass | Django Admin               |
